{"root":{"data":{"id":"dk3fed08ksg0","created":1784553440680,"text":"FineDiving：面向过程感知动作质量评估的细粒度跳水数据集"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"dk3fgw1xczc0","created":1784553638869,"text":"摘要"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"dk3fgyi142o0","created":1784553644196,"text":"研究背景"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"dk3fhaydtwo0","created":1784553671307,"text":"现有的动作质量评估方法大多依赖整个视频的深层特征来预测分数，由于推理过程不透明且可解释性差，这种方法可靠性较低"},"children":[]}]},{"data":{"id":"dk3fh0wurqw0","created":1784553649446,"text":"研究发现"},"children":[]}]}]},"template":"default","theme":"fresh-blue","version":"1.4.43"}